olly in harmony with </div><div class="t mfa x1c h35 y1d50 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">His character. </div><div class="t mb14 x70 h35 y1e39 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Christ is now dealing with the sin </div><div class="t m7d1 x1c h35 y1b8d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">problem in the most holy place of </div><div class="t m8c x58 h35 y18ca ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the heavenly sanctuary. This work </div><div class="t m7c3 x58 h35 y1872 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">will soon be finished. He will then </div><div class="t m533 x1c h35 y2045 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">confront sin on its home grounds. </div><div class="t m9da x1c h35 y1b22 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Heaven will release its unmixed fury </div><div class="t m554 x1c h35 y1fe8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">on the heads of the unsaved. The </div><div class="t m148b x1c h35 y1402 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">rebellion will be stamped out. Sin </div><div class="t m39a x1c h35 y165e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">must be eradicated. Christ must </div><div class="t mb1 x1c h35 y118d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">come! </div><div class="t mf6f x1c h49 y1a52 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">DAILY HIGHLIGHTS </div><div class="t m12c x1c h49 y1462 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m153c xae h49 y1462 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;And Receive You&quot; </div><div class="t mf45 xae h49 y2177 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(John 14:3; 2 Peter 3:10) </div><div class="t m814 x1c h49 y105e ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m18ec xae h49 y105e ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;Distress of Nations&quot; </div><div class="t m1d9d xae h49 y213c ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Luke </div><div class="t m9c3 xa3 h35 y1be7 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">21:25, 26) </div><div class="t m66d x1c h49 y1fa4 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m10f7 xae h49 y1cc0 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Defiled Earth </div><div class="t m2fa x86 h49 y1b78 ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">(Isa. 24:5, 6) </div><div class="t m7e1 x1c h49 y1a0a ff3 fs0 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">4. </div><di